{"tid":1120743,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港四大才子","createTime":"2019-04-23T01:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T14:40:49.000Z","uid":229754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"176dee4cbb82f76f8772c77d18c943b2df062d28","tid":1120743,"uid":229754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:01:18.000Z","msg":"年輕尚輕 唔係好清楚佢哋嘅事跡 所以在此拋磚引玉，希望大家不吝賜教<br />\n<br />\n只論才學，我諗金庸必然居首<br />\n其餘三人又點排？<br />\n金庸喺文學上嘅成就自不必說<br />\n倪匡為科幻小說大師，其風骨更為人祟敬<br />\n黃霑亦為一代填詞宗師<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡瀾點解可以同其餘三人並稱？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陶傑同佢哋又差幾遠？"},{"pid":"4fad68ed78cb257117caa8a8e97e93723fa2fbbf","tid":1120743,"uid":59711,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:01:51.000Z","msg":"陶傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00e69ef42127187b7d86526ba1c8ada47842262","tid":1120743,"uid":36296,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:02:32.000Z","msg":"蔡瀾既三文魚論影響左好多人"},{"pid":"df88ab32dd79be295edd4142d1b1be60d566ad3a","tid":1120743,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:04:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"bbab424df4b10749cd150315870ad8b20110fd8f","tid":1120743,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:06:37.000Z","msg":"一個識食<br />\n一個唔識食"},{"pid":"f713768bd5f94ef2074f766f90f7cc53632e1e2c","tid":1120743,"uid":229754,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b00e69ef42127187b7d86526ba1c8ada47842262","tid":1120743,"uid":36296,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:02:32.000Z","msg":"蔡瀾既三文魚論影響左好多人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"認真post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 三文魚論擁護者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0c6664c53c5ee6f34f00904828688aeb3d374e","tid":1120743,"uid":38821,"